Issue 7: Children Points Wallet API
Title
Build children points wallet system

Description
Create a points wallet system where parents can add points to children and children can spend points.

Endpoints
GET /api/points/:childId
POST /api/points/topup
POST /api/points/spend
GET /api/points/:childId/transactions
Tasks
Allow parent to give points to child
Allow child to spend points
Link points to mock bank balance
Store points transactions in PostgreSQL
Update balance after each transaction
Acceptance Criteria
Parent can add points
Child can spend points
Points balance updates correctly
Transactions are saved and visible